room_title: Escape room "Presidential Assassination" by Time Escape in Seattle
review: Great visit with the family. The Assassin room was great. A linear game style with great clues and hints. Very well laid out and staff was awesome. Don't miss this place while in town.

room_title: Escape room "Presidential Assassination" by Time Escape in Seattle
review: Presidential Assassination - threat eliminated. Goodie but tough for our novice group, would definitely revisit again.

room_title: Escape room "Presidential Assassination" by Time Escape in Seattle
review: Our family of four had a great time doing the Presidential Assassin room. The staff was super friendly and the room had quite a few unexpected elements. We would definitely recommend Time Escape Seattle!
